# S04 — FRONTEND_DEV Brief: Tuya Integration

role: FRONTEND_DEV
sprint: S04
stack: Vue 3, Vite, Tailwind, Socket.IO-client, Chart.js

tasks:
  - Add Tuya dashboard section (or unified device list with provider filter)
  - Reuse DeviceCard from S03; extend props if Tuya needs extras
  - Tuya Scene selector/executor UI (if in scope)
  - Energy chart for Tuya plugs (if API provides data)
  - Socket listener for tuya:update or unified device:update

implementation:
  - Same patterns as S03: script setup, Tailwind, dark mode
  - Provider badge/label on cards (eWeLink vs Tuya)
  - Handle Tuya-specific controls (scenes, energy) via slots or conditional UI

reusability:
  - Card remains provider-agnostic where possible
  - Chart component from S03 extended for Tuya energy

anti-patterns:
  - Duplicating card logic for Tuya
  - Hardcoded Tuya-specific logic in shared components (prefer props/slots)
